content: I haven't had a chance to explore much beyond the immediate area around my apartment, but I'm looking forward to discovering more of the neighborhood's hidden gems. There's a vintage bookstore I've been wanting to check out, and I've heard great things about a local coffee shop that's within walking distance. As for food, I'm excited to try out some of the international cuisine options – there's a Korean BBQ place and an Indian restaurant that caught my eye.
